text: Magnus Brunner (; born 6 May 1972) is an Austrian People's Party politician who has been the European Commissioner for Internal Affairs and Migration since December 2024.Francois Murphy (31 July 2024), bAustria nominates Finance Minister Brunner as European commissioner Reuters. Before, he was Austria's finance minister from 2021 until 2024. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:European Union politicians Category:Austrian politicians
